news-korea-econ.title: Trump's NIH director isn't the only one wearing multiple hats during the president's second term
news-korea-econ.description: President Donald Trump has tasked several Cabinet members and other officials with multiple roles in his second administration, most notably Secretary of State Marco Rubio.
